sql: SELECT School_id, donator_name FROM endowment WHERE amount BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR School_id NOT IN (SELECT School_id FROM budget AS e WHERE e.total_budget_percent_invested BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY donator_name ORDER BY School_id ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.County), c.School_id, c.Enrollment FROM School AS c WHERE  c.Enrollment < 32 AND Location IN (SELECT Location FROM School AS q WHERE q.Enrollment BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY c.Enrollment ORDER BY c.Enrollment DESC
SELECT w.donator_name, w.School_id FROM endowment AS w JOIN endowment ON endowment.endowment_id = w.endowment_id WHERE  w.School_id > 14 GROUP BY w.School_id ORDER BY w.School_id ASC
SELECT COUNT(School_id), COUNT(DISTINCT School_id), donator_name, School_id FROM endowment GROUP BY School_id
SELECT SUM(m.Enrollment), COUNT(m.Enrollment), SUM(m.Enrollment), m.IHSAA_Class FROM School AS m WHERE  m.Enrollment > 1 GROUP BY m.IHSAA_Class

SELECT Budget_invested_percent FROM budget WHERE  total_budget_percent_budgeted >= 64 AND Budgeted NOT IN (SELECT Budgeted FROM budget WHERE  total_budget_percent_budgeted > 94 LIMIT 2) ORDER BY Budget_invested_percent ASC
SELECT IHSAA_Class FROM School JOIN budget JOIN endowment ON School.School_id = budget.School_id AND endowment.School_id = School.School_id ORDER BY IHSAA_Class ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT Enrollment FROM School

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n.IHSAA_Football_Class), n.Location, n.IHSAA_Class FROM School AS n WHERE n.Enrollment BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Mascot = (SELECT MAX(Mascot) FROM School AS t WHERE  t.Enrollment = 33 LIMIT 7)
SELECT AVG(endowment_id), donator_name FROM endowment WHERE  endowment_id >= 10 OR School_id NOT IN (SELECT School_id FROM budget WHERE  Budgeted > 93)

SELECT AVG(a.amount), endowment.endowment_id, a.amount, endowment.amount FROM endowment AS a JOIN endowment ON endowment.endowment_id = a.endowment_id WHERE amount >= (SELECT AVG(amount) FROM endowment WHERE  amount > 98) GROUP BY endowment.amount HAVING COUNT(a.endowment_id) = 93 ORDER BY endowment.amount ASC
SELECT Year, Budgeted FROM School JOIN budget ON School.School_id = budget.School_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM endowment WHERE  School_id < 9 AND School.School_id = School_id) ORDER BY Year DESC

SELECT total_budget_percent_invested, endowment.School_id FROM School JOIN budget JOIN endowment ON School.School_id = budget.School_id AND endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  total_budget_percent_invested <= 23 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM School WHERE  Enrollment > 53 AND budget.School_id = School_id) ORDER BY total_budget_percent_invested ASC
SELECT amount, IHSAA_Class FROM School JOIN endowment ON endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  endowment_id < 11 GROUP BY IHSAA_Class HAVING COUNT(amount) > 25 ORDER BY IHSAA_Class DESC
SELECT y.total_budget_percent_invested, y.Budget_invested_percent, y.Budgeted FROM budget AS y WHERE y.Year BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY y.Budgeted HAVING MAX(y.total_budget_percent_invested) >= 4
SELECT MAX(b.endowment_id), endowment.donator_name FROM endowment AS b JOIN endowment ON endowment.endowment_id = b.endowment_id
SELECT Enrollment FROM School JOIN endowment ON endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  Enrollment >= 86 ORDER BY Enrollment DESC

SELECT AVG(Enrollment), Enrollment FROM School WHERE Enrollment BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM endowment AS h WHERE School.School_id = h.School_id LIMIT 6) GROUP BY Enrollment HAVING AVG(Enrollment) > 52 ORDER BY Enrollment ASC
SELECT MIN(endowment_id) FROM School JOIN endowment ON endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  Enrollment != 44

SELECT total_budget_percent_invested, Budget_invested_percent, total_budget_percent_budgeted FROM budget WHERE  total_budget_percent_invested != 35 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM School WHERE  Enrollment > 26 AND budget.School_id = School_id LIMIT 8) GROUP BY total_budget_percent_budgeted HAVING MIN(Budgeted) = 57 LIMIT 1

SELECT Enrollment, total_budget_percent_invested, total_budget_percent_budgeted FROM School JOIN budget JOIN endowment ON School.School_id = budget.School_id AND endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  amount = 96 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM School WHERE Enrollment BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND budget.School_id = School_id) GROUP BY total_budget_percent_budgeted HAVING MAX(Budgeted) > 30 LIMIT 6

SELECT b.donator_name FROM endowment AS b JOIN endowment ON endowment.endowment_id = b.endowment_id WHERE donator_name >= (SELECT MIN(donator_name) FROM endowment WHERE School_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) LIMIT 1

SELECT Enrollment, amount FROM School JOIN budget JOIN endowment ON School.School_id = budget.School_id AND endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  Budgeted != 72 GROUP BY amount ORDER BY Enrollment DESC
SELECT Enrollment FROM School WHERE  Enrollment < 70

SELECT Enrollment, Location FROM School JOIN endowment ON endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE  endowment_id < 54 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM School WHERE  Enrollment < 57 AND endowment.endowment_id = School_id)
SELECT COUNT(z.Budgeted), z.Budget_invested_percent FROM budget AS z
SELECT School_id, donator_name FROM endowment WHERE  endowment_id >= 44 GROUP BY donator_name HAVING SUM(endowment_id) > 90
SELECT SUM(n.total_budget_percent_budgeted), n.Invested, n.School_id FROM budget AS n WHERE  n.Budgeted != 84
SELECT donator_name FROM endowment ORDER BY donator_name DESC
SELECT Budget_invested_percent FROM budget WHERE  total_budget_percent_budgeted = 41 ORDER BY Budget_invested_percent DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT AVG(endowment_id), endowment_id FROM School JOIN endowment ON endowment.School_id = School.School_id WHERE amount IN (SELECT amount FROM endowment AS g WHERE  g.amount > 2) ORDER BY endowment_id DESC
